Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,上學去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,上學去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs54}第一節課好像是魔法藥學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs54}還是治療魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs54}那個看起來真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,您早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,古蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 原來你在這裡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,早 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,安 安公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 古蕾雅好歹也是龍族的公主呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我安就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我們之前一起借的書
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是我推薦給你的那本書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒讀完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我讀懂了瑪娜利亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不 讀懂了安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那本書很有趣 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡的圖書館裡有各種語言的書
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,藏書室也有好多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,會想要全都讀個遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,說來前幾天我還找到了龍之國的書
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,古蕾雅的國家是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,和這裡不同 有好多巨型動物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 那可真是個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那你為什麼要來這裡上學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是我媽媽的母校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是人龍混血兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 原來你媽媽也是這裡的學生呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,安學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,安學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,露
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝啦 安學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,藏書室裡出了大事 您快來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}古蕾雅 抱歉 等我會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,漢娜 沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我不該踩它 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,大家退後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我能封印它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,寒冰束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不怪您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這不怪公主您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是我讓您封印藏書室領主的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但漢娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至幫不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,算哪門子會長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,能力不足 真窩囊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不配為會長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,要是還有什麼事需要我幫忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,今天已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,古…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,古蕾雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,忙完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,封印之後都凍住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,藏書室領主生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,雷霆大怒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在收拾我留下的爛攤子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,而我卻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你盡力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說你一直在等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但你也讓我等太久了…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,安 你肚子餓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,說來我一早開始就沒吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你想吃甜的還是辣的 古蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,甜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,果然 其實我也想吃甜的
